data.description: Welcome Home! You will enjoy the well laid out floor plan that has that open concept. Cook in the well appointed kitchen while you entertain your guest while they sit at the large granite island. There is plenty of storage and counters to easily store all your culinary tools. This home has 3 bedrooms 2 baths an office and bonus space for kids with built in desk. Primary bedroom is spacious with a large bath to match. The back patio is covered and roomy enough to enjoy those evening cocktails. Sellers have already found there next home and ready to welcome you to make this yours.
